      "description": "Honest little runabout being sold as a budget-friendly car for someone who needs simple, affordable transport or a project to tinker with. It\u2019s not a showroom car, but it has plenty of character and could be a great fit for a handy owner, first-time buyer on a tight budget, or anyone after a cheap set of wheels. Priced to reflect its condition and to sell, so if you\u2019re looking for value over perfection, this one is well worth a look.",
