      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly project or daily-with-character. Runs, drives, and has the kind of straightforward mechanical layout enthusiasts appreciate for easy wrenching and affordable upkeep. Not a showroom car and shows its age, but it offers dependable core transportation with good parts value, practical utility, and plenty of potential for someone who wants an inexpensive platform to sort, improve, or just drive as-is.",
