      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, road-worn character you can\u2019t fake\u2014a budget-friendly ride with plenty of story left in it. Whether you want an inexpensive set of wheels, a practical backup vehicle, or a hands-on project with real personality, this one offers a rare chance to get in cheap and make it your own. It\u2019s the sort of car for someone who sees possibility where others just see age: a machine with grit, presence, and room for a fresh chapter.",
